.de PI	\" Picture Include
.	\" $1=file(page) $2=height,width,yoff,xoff $3=flags
.	\" Height, width, xoff, and yoff are for the frame, flags is for the
.	\" picture. Default dimensions are inches.
\\X'PI:\\n(.o:\\n(.i:\\n(.l:\\n(.t:\\$1:\\$2:\\$3:'\\c
